    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cardinal Sequence</strong> is a cosmic rogue-lite deckbuilder with a unique twist: cards are played by inputting sequences of directional commands. Chain together powerful abilities, discover incredible synergies and master a whole new way to play cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/6bea7b6e26f666503054778224ebc4a8.poster.avif?t=1753559732\" width=800 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/6bea7b6e26f666503054778224ebc4a8.webm?t=1753559732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/6bea7b6e26f666503054778224ebc4a8.mp4?t=1753559732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A New Way to Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hand is your command console. In <strong>Cardinal Sequence</strong>, you input patterns of ↑, ↓, ←, → to activate your cards. Master the system to produce points, trigger special effects, chain combos and uncover new tactical layers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/18db9a64a087e71bbe571087d1e76649.poster.avif?t=1753559732\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/18db9a64a087e71bbe571087d1e76649.webm?t=1753559732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/18db9a64a087e71bbe571087d1e76649.mp4?t=1753559732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game-Breaking Luck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get lucky - and break the game.  Make use of rare variants and hidden legendary cards to blow up your scores and pass ever increasing challenges. Every run has the potential to breach the speed of light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/87ae33ba79c3788ff2844ed24a8fe3a2.poster.avif?t=1753559732\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/87ae33ba79c3788ff2844ed24a8fe3a2.webm?t=1753559732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331370/extras/87ae33ba79c3788ff2844ed24a8fe3a2.mp4?t=1753559732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover Unique Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a large arsenal of cards by conquering higher difficulties and achievements. Each one introduces new mechanics, powerful effects and synergy opportunities that can reshape your strategy with every run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Empowering Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn tokens to acquire permanent upgrades that supercharge your runs, open new strategies and give you a shot at conquering all 10 escalating difficulty tiers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relaxing Space Theme</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chill in hyperspace. With its calming atmosphere, ambient sci-fi music, and cosmic visuals, <strong>Cardinal Sequence</strong> invites you to take your time, plot your path, and drift among the stars as you chase the perfect sequence.</p>",
